### =========================================
### EXEMPLOS DE API - SISTEMA DE AGENDAMENTO
### =========================================

### 1. Listar todas as consultas
GET http://localhost:3001/appointments

### 2. Buscar consulta por ID (substitua pelo ID real)
GET http://localhost:3001/appointments/CONSULTA_ID_AQUI

### 3. Criar nova consulta
POST http://localhost:3001/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": "1",
  "date": "2024-01-30",
  "time": "14:00",
  "duration": 60,
  "procedure": "Consulta de rotina",
  "professional": "Dr. Ana Silva",
  "status": "pendente",
  "notes": "Consulta criada via API"
}

### 4. Atualizar consulta (substitua pelo ID real)
PUT http://localhost:3001/appointments/CONSULTA_ID_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmado",
  "notes": "Consulta confirmada pelo paciente"
}

### 5. Verificar disponibilidade de horário
POST http://localhost:3001/appointments/check-availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-01-30",
  "time": "15:00",
  "professional": "Dr. Ana Silva"
}

### 6. Buscar horários disponíveis
GET http://localhost:3001/appointments/available-times?date=2024-01-30&professional=Dr. Ana Silva

### 7. Buscar horários disponíveis (qualquer profissional)
GET http://localhost:3001/appointments/available-times?date=2024-01-30

### 8. Buscar consultas por paciente
GET http://localhost:3001/appointments/patient/1

### 9. Buscar consultas da próxima hora (para N8N)
GET http://localhost:3001/appointments/next-hour

### 10. Confirmar consulta via WhatsApp (para N8N)
PUT http://localhost:3001/appointments/CONSULTA_ID_AQUI/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirmed": true
}

### 11. Cancelar consulta via WhatsApp (para N8N)  
PUT http://localhost:3001/appointments/CONSULTA_ID_AQUI/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirmed": false
}

### 12. Remover consulta
DELETE http://localhost:3001/appointments/CONSULTA_ID_AQUI

